Name: Zolux Bird Feeding Station, Black 188cm
Description:
Zolux Bird Feeding Station, Black 188cm

A bird feeding station is a structure designed to hold multiple bird feeders, allowing you to serve a variety of treats for a range of different bird species at once.
You can customize your feeding station with feeders to suit the birds you want to attract and place it in your garden. 
A plain wooden platform can be erected as a simple feeding station.
Some edging around the outside will help keep the seed from falling to the ground.
A bird feeding station is an excellent way to display your feeders and creates the perfect feeding environment for your birds.

Contains:

3 Hooks to hang your feeders or birds house
1 Transparent plate
1 Mesh plate

Total length 188 cm
